WEBVTT

01:51.960 --> 01:53.200
Doctor, how is she?

01:54.160 --> 01:56.840
The patient's condition suddenly worsened during the surgery.

01:56.840 --> 01:57.720
I'm afraid

01:58.039 --> 02:00.040
she won't make it through the night.

02:20.000 --> 02:22.000
Yuanbao.

02:23.200 --> 02:25.440
Grandma, I'm here.

02:29.600 --> 02:30.280
Grandma.

02:30.920 --> 02:33.000
I promised Mom and Dad

02:33.640 --> 02:35.320
to take good care of you.

02:36.560 --> 02:38.120
You also promised me

02:38.720 --> 02:40.320
that when I get married,

02:41.120 --> 02:43.000
you'd help me dress up.

02:45.360 --> 02:47.490
And when I have children in the future,

02:47.720 --> 02:49.800
you'd help me take care of them.

02:52.480 --> 02:53.920
We agreed.

02:55.640 --> 02:57.520
You will live a long life.

02:58.120 --> 03:00.560
You will always stay with me.

03:02.720 --> 03:03.560
Grandma.

03:04.400 --> 03:05.720
When you get better,

03:07.320 --> 03:09.120
I'll go home for dinner.

03:10.280 --> 03:13.160
I still want to eat the spare ribs you make.

03:15.520 --> 03:16.880
Yuanbao.

03:18.800 --> 03:20.360
Let go of the past.

03:22.160 --> 03:23.720
Cherish what you have.

03:24.600 --> 03:26.320
Be grateful.

03:27.920 --> 03:29.880
Live a good life.

03:31.480 --> 03:33.200
Grandma loves you.

03:34.520 --> 03:36.440
Grandma will be in heaven,

03:38.120 --> 03:39.720
staying by your side,

03:40.720 --> 03:42.160
and blessing you.

03:43.600 --> 03:44.960
No, Grandma.

03:45.600 --> 03:47.920
Mom and Dad are already gone.

03:48.480 --> 03:50.560
Don't leave Yuanbao behind.

03:51.440 --> 03:52.360
Grandma!

04:08.880 --> 04:10.080
Grandma!

04:11.080 --> 04:12.120
Grandma!

04:13.280 --> 04:15.360
Grandma!

04:17.519 --> 04:18.959
Grandma!

04:20.600 --> 04:22.079
Then when I get married...

04:22.320 --> 04:24.200
You have to dress me up

04:24.440 --> 04:26.160
and make me look beautiful.

04:27.960 --> 04:28.760
Okay.

04:29.120 --> 04:33.200
I'm just looking forward to the day you find happiness.

04:52.040 --> 04:52.880
No!

04:53.400 --> 04:55.560
Where are you taking my grandma?

04:55.840 --> 04:58.920
Where are you taking her?

04:58.960 --> 04:59.800
Yuanbao.

05:00.600 --> 05:02.480
Your grandma won't rest in peace if you act like this.

05:02.480 --> 05:03.440
You can't be like this.

05:03.440 --> 05:04.800
Let go, Yuanbao.

05:05.200 --> 05:06.240
Grandma!

05:07.760 --> 05:09.760
Please let go, Yuanbao.

05:11.560 --> 05:12.240
Doctor.

05:13.120 --> 05:15.000
Doctor, please save my grandma.

05:15.040 --> 05:17.200
I'm begging you, save my grandma.

05:17.480 --> 05:19.640
My grandma is not dead.

05:19.760 --> 05:21.680
She is not dead yet.

05:21.680 --> 05:25.010
My grandma said she would wait for me to come home for dinner.

05:25.960 --> 05:28.080
The dead cannot be brought back to life. My condolences.

05:28.080 --> 05:29.520
My grandma is all I have.

05:29.520 --> 05:31.320
Let go, child.

05:39.920 --> 05:40.760
Mutou.

05:43.240 --> 05:44.800
Yuanbao, Yuanbao.

05:44.800 --> 05:45.920
She's too emotional.

05:45.920 --> 05:47.850
Hurry, take her to the ward to rest.

05:52.880 --> 05:56.400
Mom, what are you guys doing?

05:57.000 --> 05:59.360
Why are you just coming back now?

06:01.960 --> 06:02.840
Who is that?

06:05.960 --> 06:07.490
I'm asking you, who is that?

06:13.560 --> 06:14.560
It's Grandma.

06:16.280 --> 06:17.120
Grandma...

06:23.400 --> 06:24.160
My child.

06:25.240 --> 06:26.520
Grandma, I'm back.

06:26.920 --> 06:27.520
Grandma.

06:28.080 --> 06:29.840
I won the prize money.

06:30.280 --> 06:32.040
I can pay for your treatment.

06:32.400 --> 06:35.159
You'll get better after the surgery.

06:36.120 --> 06:37.120
Grandma,

06:37.680 --> 06:41.280
you promised Yuanbao you'd take care of her forever.

06:41.360 --> 06:42.240
Didn't you?

06:43.440 --> 06:44.800
Grandma!

06:45.760 --> 06:46.680
Grandma,

06:47.760 --> 06:49.080
look at me.

06:50.240 --> 06:51.880
My child, don't be like this.

06:52.280 --> 06:55.120
Grandma won't rest in peace if you do.

06:55.800 --> 06:56.240
My child.

06:56.240 --> 06:57.720
Grandma!

06:59.240 --> 07:01.480
I won the prize money.

07:02.160 --> 07:04.640
I can pay for your treatment and surgery.

07:04.800 --> 07:06.040
Grandma,

07:06.680 --> 07:08.480
look at me.

07:47.680 --> 07:48.440
Yuanbao,

07:49.360 --> 07:50.320
you're awake.

07:53.600 --> 07:55.800
The doctor said you were overly grieved

07:56.040 --> 07:57.760
and physically exhausted.

07:58.800 --> 08:00.860
I've asked Ms. Tian for leave for you.

08:01.000 --> 08:02.440
Get some good rest.

08:03.160 --> 08:03.920
Yuanbao,

08:04.960 --> 08:06.820
grandma's funeral arrangements

08:06.920 --> 08:08.850
will be handled by your aunt and me.

08:09.560 --> 08:11.360
Take good care of yourself,

08:12.240 --> 08:13.840
so she won't worry about you.

08:26.640 --> 08:27.400
Qingyun,

08:28.000 --> 08:28.960
your dad and I

08:28.960 --> 08:31.090
need to take care of grandma's funeral

08:31.240 --> 08:32.570
and look after Yuanbao.

08:33.320 --> 08:35.000
You've been tired for days,

08:35.440 --> 08:36.799
go home and rest.

08:37.640 --> 08:38.880
We've got this.

08:42.200 --> 08:44.600
Green garlic is quite expensive nowadays.

09:05.680 --> 09:06.920
Time to eat.

09:16.280 --> 09:17.280
Grandma.

10:17.640 --> 10:18.320
Qingyun.

10:18.600 --> 10:19.320
Qingyun.

11:10.240 --> 11:12.480
How are the school procedures going?

11:13.880 --> 11:16.680
Both kids' previous applications were rejected.

11:17.720 --> 11:20.120
I just faxed over the documents of Qingyun's

11:20.120 --> 11:22.560
national physics competition award.

11:23.440 --> 11:24.520
Let's wait and see.

11:29.200 --> 11:30.330
What about Yuanbao?

11:33.120 --> 11:34.650
Let's try our best for both.

11:35.240 --> 11:37.640
We can't miss such a good opportunity.

11:40.240 --> 11:41.880
I hope there will be two spots.

11:41.880 --> 11:43.280
There must be two spots.

11:50.680 --> 11:51.520
This child

11:52.400 --> 11:54.520
hasn't slept well for days.

11:55.240 --> 11:56.360
Don't wake him up.

12:32.240 --> 12:33.080
Grandma.

12:55.800 --> 12:58.520
Grandma, you must live a long life

12:58.800 --> 13:00.120
and stay with me forever.

13:00.120 --> 13:03.560
Okay, Grandma will live a long life

13:03.880 --> 13:06.160
and stay with you forever.

13:22.360 --> 13:24.240
Come on, Yuanbao.

13:24.680 --> 13:25.960
You are the best.

13:26.320 --> 13:27.040
Yuanbao,

13:27.600 --> 13:28.360
come on.

13:30.120 --> 13:31.760
You are the best.

13:43.920 --> 13:44.760
Grandma,

13:49.480 --> 13:50.800
we are going home.

15:23.520 --> 15:26.640
Yuanbao, will you come to the UK with us?

15:29.840 --> 15:31.720
To study abroad with Qingyun.

15:32.120 --> 15:33.680
We've looked into it.

15:33.960 --> 15:36.480
You can take a one-year foundation course first,

15:36.480 --> 15:37.680
and then apply for university.

15:37.680 --> 15:38.610
I'm not leaving.

15:41.680 --> 15:42.600
Why?

15:44.560 --> 15:46.400
I can't leave my grandma behind.

15:50.760 --> 15:51.480
Yuanbao.

15:55.080 --> 15:56.640
I understand how you feel,

15:57.960 --> 16:00.020
but the dead cannot come back to life.

16:02.240 --> 16:03.640
The living

16:04.880 --> 16:07.160
must live well for those who have passed.

16:07.480 --> 16:09.080
I think your parents

16:10.480 --> 16:12.360
and your grandma in heaven

16:13.800 --> 16:16.400
would want you to be with us.

16:24.000 --> 16:25.160
I know that in your heart,

16:25.160 --> 16:27.420
you've never forgiven your uncle and me.

16:27.960 --> 16:28.880
I also know that

16:30.160 --> 16:31.760
if it weren't for us,

16:32.640 --> 16:35.170
your family wouldn't have ended up like this.

16:41.240 --> 16:42.880
It was right in this room

16:46.040 --> 16:48.700
that your uncle and I knelt before your grandma,

16:48.720 --> 16:51.180
confessing and asking for her forgiveness.

16:55.600 --> 16:56.760
Grandma, she...

16:58.440 --> 16:59.320
knew.

17:02.360 --> 17:04.680
We came to tell her after it happened,

17:04.760 --> 17:07.040
but she already knew by then.

17:11.880 --> 17:13.240
Grandma did all this

17:17.280 --> 17:18.800
for me.

17:20.599 --> 17:21.880
Silly child.

17:23.480 --> 17:25.010
You could say it was for you,

17:25.119 --> 17:27.520
but mostly, she wanted us who are still alive

17:27.520 --> 17:29.640
to live well, my child.

17:31.320 --> 17:33.320
Before your father died,

17:35.840 --> 17:37.360
he told your Uncle Mu,

17:38.440 --> 17:41.720
"Take care of my mom and Yuanbao for me.

17:43.200 --> 17:48.360
Don't tell the children about today's accident."

17:52.680 --> 17:53.520
Grandma.

17:54.760 --> 17:55.800
Mom and Dad.

17:57.080 --> 17:58.240
Don't worry.

17:59.320 --> 18:01.040
I will live well

18:01.720 --> 18:03.250
so you won't worry about me.

18:04.240 --> 18:05.080
But

18:06.120 --> 18:08.760
I can't drag down Qingyun's family anymore.

18:10.400 --> 18:11.400
You are right.

18:11.920 --> 18:13.120
It was an accident.

18:14.160 --> 18:15.160
No one is to blame.

18:17.280 --> 18:18.120
Auntie.

18:20.560 --> 18:21.680
You should go.

18:23.240 --> 18:24.320
I won't leave.

18:25.000 --> 18:26.400
I am grown up now.

18:27.360 --> 18:28.800
I can be independent.

18:29.760 --> 18:31.560
You don't need to worry about me.

18:32.200 --> 18:35.840
I hope Mutou can have a better life.

18:36.440 --> 18:38.200
But you alone.

18:38.240 --> 18:39.640
I don't hate you anymore,

18:39.720 --> 18:40.600
really.

18:42.760 --> 18:43.960
I just

18:44.880 --> 18:47.040
can't bear to leave my mom and dad,

18:47.960 --> 18:49.120
and my grandma.

18:51.800 --> 18:53.600
My home is here.

18:55.160 --> 18:56.720
This is my home.

18:59.560 --> 19:01.480
So I won't go abroad.

19:06.800 --> 19:07.760
Yuanbao.

19:28.320 --> 19:31.650
What do you mean there's only one quota for studying abroad?

19:32.040 --> 19:33.700
Since there is only one quota,

19:33.760 --> 19:34.960
why bother?

19:35.560 --> 19:36.040
I,

19:36.320 --> 19:36.720
we,

19:36.920 --> 19:37.480
why don't

19:37.960 --> 19:39.440
we just stay in China?

19:39.520 --> 19:40.840
Why must we go to the UK?

19:41.840 --> 19:43.520
I talked to Yuanbao too.

19:44.400 --> 19:47.130
She can take a one-year foundation course first.

19:48.040 --> 19:49.000
But she,

19:51.040 --> 19:52.700
she absolutely refused to go.

19:53.600 --> 19:56.240
But this is too important to you.

19:56.640 --> 19:58.680
If you graduate from that university,

19:58.680 --> 20:00.480
your future will be boundless.

20:00.880 --> 20:03.040
This is the most important thing in your life.

20:03.040 --> 20:04.480
What about Yuanbao?

20:05.720 --> 20:07.180
Grandma just passed away.

20:07.840 --> 20:09.160
If we leave too,

20:09.520 --> 20:11.520
are we going to leave her here alone?

20:11.680 --> 20:12.540
I don't want to.

20:13.160 --> 20:13.800
Son.

20:14.800 --> 20:16.360
We really have no choice.

20:16.480 --> 20:18.210
We really can't get two quotas.

20:18.400 --> 20:19.080
Otherwise,

20:19.520 --> 20:21.600
we wouldn't leave Yuanbao behind.

20:22.600 --> 20:23.840
Mom, Dad,

20:24.080 --> 20:24.760
believe me.

20:25.080 --> 20:26.340
Even if I stay in China,

20:26.360 --> 20:28.200
I can definitely get into a very good university

20:28.200 --> 20:29.440
and have a bright future.

20:29.440 --> 20:30.960
Why do we have to go to the UK?

20:30.960 --> 20:32.400
Isn't our country good enough?

20:32.400 --> 20:34.800
Foreign countries are nowhere near as good as ours.

20:34.800 --> 20:36.480
Besides, we absolutely cannot leave.

20:36.480 --> 20:38.280
If we really leave, what about Yuanbao?

20:38.280 --> 20:39.210
She's all alone.

20:39.240 --> 20:41.640
Why are you so stubborn?

20:42.640 --> 20:44.570
We didn't say we'd never come back.

20:45.120 --> 20:46.240
As long as you're on holiday,

20:46.240 --> 20:47.040
I promise you,

20:47.480 --> 20:48.960
whether it's winter or summer vacation,

20:48.960 --> 20:50.560
we will come back to see her.

20:51.280 --> 20:53.200
Besides, if Yuanbao works hard,

20:53.240 --> 20:55.370
she can get into her ideal university.

20:55.480 --> 20:57.280
And in less than a year,

20:57.720 --> 20:58.480
after a year,

20:58.480 --> 20:59.640
wouldn't the two of you

20:59.640 --> 21:01.760
go your separate ways to university anyway?

21:01.760 --> 21:03.400
That's different, Mom.

21:03.520 --> 21:04.520
I told Yuanbao that

21:04.520 --> 21:05.840
we are family.

21:06.320 --> 21:08.180
Now we're leaving her here alone.

21:08.280 --> 21:09.680
Her grandma passed away,

21:09.720 --> 21:11.120
Grandpa Gong went to the nursing home,

21:11.120 --> 21:12.180
and we're not here.

21:12.200 --> 21:13.200
She's just a girl,

21:13.280 --> 21:14.320
all alone here.

21:14.560 --> 21:15.320
If she gets sick

21:15.320 --> 21:17.120
or has an accident, who will take care of her?

21:17.120 --> 21:18.840
How can you be so cruel?

21:19.000 --> 21:20.200
Cruel?

21:21.200 --> 21:23.080
We tried our best

21:23.160 --> 21:24.690
to fight for quotas for you.

21:24.920 --> 21:26.880
If you hadn't won the physics competition,

21:26.880 --> 21:28.740
you wouldn't be able to go either.

21:29.160 --> 21:30.160
For Yuanbao,

21:30.560 --> 21:32.840
your father and I have done our best

21:32.880 --> 21:34.560
and given her everything.

21:34.920 --> 21:36.280
For Grandma's medical bills,

21:36.280 --> 21:36.680
we...

21:36.680 --> 21:37.440
Qiuling.

21:37.960 --> 21:38.680
Qiuling.

21:43.600 --> 21:44.800
Even if we go abroad,

21:45.240 --> 21:45.880
your father and I

21:45.880 --> 21:47.400
will find a way to leave Yuanbao

21:47.400 --> 21:48.720
enough money for food

21:48.760 --> 21:50.480
and tuition.

21:50.840 --> 21:52.200
What else do you want us to do

21:52.200 --> 21:53.640
to satisfy you?

21:56.520 --> 21:59.960
Mom, you said it yourself before.

22:00.840 --> 22:02.920
Yuanbao is your own daughter.

22:04.080 --> 22:05.210
Have you forgotten?

22:06.400 --> 22:08.840
Now you're leaving her here all alone.

22:10.200 --> 22:13.200
If it weren't for Uncle Xiong and the others back then...

22:13.200 --> 22:15.280
Would I be the one left behind now?

22:15.680 --> 22:16.240
You...

22:16.320 --> 22:18.280
How can you two be so ungrateful?

22:19.680 --> 22:20.480
Enough.

22:22.880 --> 22:24.760
Child, how can you talk like that?

22:24.880 --> 22:27.210
How can you speak to your parents this way?

22:28.000 --> 22:28.960
You are right.

22:30.480 --> 22:32.940
If it weren't for your Uncle Xiong back then,

22:33.240 --> 22:35.240
you would be the one left behind now.

22:35.560 --> 22:36.880
But even so,

22:38.040 --> 22:40.300
just because we feel guilty towards you,

22:40.760 --> 22:43.560
shouldn't Yuanbao have a better future?

22:46.000 --> 22:47.000
Without Yuanbao.

22:48.600 --> 22:49.520
A future?

22:51.200 --> 22:52.860
How can there be a good future?

23:06.560 --> 23:07.160
Honey.

23:07.440 --> 23:08.560
Don't be mad.

23:09.320 --> 23:10.440
I'll go check on him.

23:10.440 --> 23:12.640
If worse comes to worst, we'll find another way.

23:12.640 --> 23:14.040
Get some rest first.

23:14.920 --> 23:15.720
Qingyun.

23:16.920 --> 23:17.640
Qingyun.

23:20.760 --> 23:21.440
Qingyun.

24:29.800 --> 24:32.560
We've lived here for 20 years.

24:33.640 --> 24:36.280
Yeah, it's getting old.

24:36.840 --> 24:38.570
When your mom and I got married,

24:38.720 --> 24:40.000
we lived here.

24:41.040 --> 24:43.500
We were neighbors with the Xiongs back then.

24:44.800 --> 24:47.120
In a blink of an eye, 20 years have passed.

24:48.800 --> 24:49.730
Unfortunately,

24:50.600 --> 24:51.680
it won't be long

24:52.120 --> 24:53.980
before this is no longer our home.

24:59.240 --> 25:01.040
What do you mean?

25:04.520 --> 25:07.280
To pay for Yuanbao's grandmother's medical bills,

25:07.280 --> 25:08.610
your mom sold the house.

25:12.440 --> 25:14.880
We have to move out early next month.

25:19.760 --> 25:20.520
I know

25:21.680 --> 25:23.080
you have some complaints

25:23.160 --> 25:24.720
about your mom.

25:26.400 --> 25:27.400
But son,

25:28.760 --> 25:29.890
anyone in this world

25:30.280 --> 25:32.880
can complain about her and misunderstand her,

25:33.280 --> 25:34.440
except for you.

25:35.760 --> 25:37.020
You were five that year

25:38.640 --> 25:40.570
and suddenly got acute pneumonia.

25:41.360 --> 25:43.240
To take care of you,

25:43.360 --> 25:46.280
your mom and I had to

25:46.560 --> 25:49.080
temporarily switch shifts with Mr. Xiong and his wife.

25:49.080 --> 25:50.740
After the accident happened,

25:51.120 --> 25:53.240
I had to handle their funerals

25:53.920 --> 25:56.400
and take care of Yuanbao and her grandmother.

25:56.400 --> 25:59.120
At the same time, I had to keep working to earn money.

25:59.120 --> 26:00.680
I simply had no time

26:01.440 --> 26:03.640
to go to the hospital to take care of you.

26:04.160 --> 26:06.360
So your mom stayed in the hospital alone

26:07.120 --> 26:10.250
and took care of you round the clock for over half a month.

26:10.880 --> 26:12.210
During that half month,

26:12.680 --> 26:14.080
she lost over ten pounds.

26:14.520 --> 26:16.250
She was completely exhausted.

26:21.960 --> 26:22.680
Later,

26:23.400 --> 26:25.330
to support two kids and an elderly,

26:26.400 --> 26:28.600
I had to go on business trips frequently

26:28.800 --> 26:30.320
to earn more money.

26:30.880 --> 26:33.340
So the heavy burden of taking care of you guys

26:33.640 --> 26:35.480
fell on your mom's shoulders.

26:37.640 --> 26:40.280
Before she married me and gave birth to you,

26:41.480 --> 26:43.760
she couldn't even boil noodles without burning the pot.

26:43.760 --> 26:44.880
But for our family,

26:45.120 --> 26:47.600
she forced herself to learn everything.

26:57.160 --> 26:59.480
She might not be an excellent woman,

27:00.120 --> 27:00.880
but

27:01.320 --> 27:03.360
she is truly an excellent mother.

27:09.360 --> 27:10.360
For so many years,

27:11.200 --> 27:12.200
your mom and I

27:12.240 --> 27:14.600
have always felt guilty

27:15.680 --> 27:17.540
trying to repay the Xiong family.

27:18.040 --> 27:19.720
We really tried our best.

27:23.640 --> 27:25.040
Choosing to go abroad now

27:25.640 --> 27:27.640
is because as your parents,

27:27.880 --> 27:29.960
we hope to do what we can

27:30.280 --> 27:32.140
to give you a better environment.

27:33.000 --> 27:34.660
But in the current situation,

27:35.520 --> 27:37.600
we really can't afford it.

27:41.920 --> 27:44.280
Going abroad doesn't mean I'll definitely be successful.

27:44.280 --> 27:46.120
We can stay in the country.

27:46.280 --> 27:47.540
It's really good here.

27:47.720 --> 27:48.360
Son,

27:48.760 --> 27:51.220
we almost don't even have a place to live now.

27:51.480 --> 27:53.740
Do you want us to live at Yuanbao's house?

27:53.920 --> 27:56.040
She knows the truth now.

27:57.920 --> 27:58.600
Tell me,

28:00.640 --> 28:02.480
how can we act like nothing happened

28:02.480 --> 28:04.140
and continue to live with her?

28:08.280 --> 28:09.720
It's all my fault.

28:11.560 --> 28:13.160
If I were more capable,

28:14.320 --> 28:17.050
we wouldn't have to make such a difficult choice.

28:26.720 --> 28:27.850
Dad, I'm sorry, Dad.

28:28.320 --> 28:29.240
I'm sorry.

28:48.560 --> 28:50.800
You must be tired. Get some rest early.

28:51.440 --> 28:53.560
Qingyun has to go to school tomorrow morning.

28:53.560 --> 28:54.440
Go to sleep.

29:05.280 --> 29:07.040
I'm sorry.

29:11.120 --> 29:12.240
But I...

29:16.360 --> 29:17.240
I'm sorry.

29:21.600 --> 29:22.360
Son.

29:24.600 --> 29:26.240
Does your face still hurt?

29:30.440 --> 29:32.600
Mom is also sorry.

29:36.600 --> 29:38.000
I've thought it through.

29:39.720 --> 29:41.920
You decide whether you want to go or not.

29:43.800 --> 29:45.360
If you decide not to go,

29:47.200 --> 29:49.480
your dad will come back to look for a job.

29:50.680 --> 29:52.960
As long as our family is together,

29:55.000 --> 29:57.240
we can live a good life.

30:33.560 --> 30:34.560
I'm sorry.

30:49.960 --> 30:51.160
Hello. Table for one?

30:52.480 --> 30:53.760
I'm expecting a friend.

30:53.760 --> 30:54.600
He'll be here soon.

30:54.600 --> 30:55.800
Okay. Please take a seat.

30:55.800 --> 30:56.440
Okay.

31:29.080 --> 31:30.880
Happy birthday, Ruirui.

31:49.720 --> 31:50.320
Ruirui.

31:50.800 --> 31:52.960
My mom is quite strict

31:53.000 --> 31:54.200
with my pocket money.

31:54.240 --> 31:55.320
So for your birthday,

31:55.320 --> 31:57.040
I could only make you a bowl of longevity noodles.

31:57.040 --> 31:57.680
Um...

31:58.880 --> 31:59.920
Don't be picky.

32:01.760 --> 32:02.600
Why would I?

32:03.280 --> 32:05.010
I love eating noodles the most.

32:06.480 --> 32:07.160
Try it.

32:18.960 --> 32:19.720
Is it good?

32:21.360 --> 32:22.000
It is.

32:22.240 --> 32:23.570
It's really delicious.

32:24.400 --> 32:25.460
Really delicious.

32:27.160 --> 32:28.360
According to you,

32:28.440 --> 32:30.570
not only can I be a singer or a comedian,

32:30.600 --> 32:32.000
but I can also be a chef.

32:33.400 --> 32:34.960
You know I'm pretty clumsy.

32:35.720 --> 32:38.400
I learned from the chef in the kitchen for a whole day

32:38.400 --> 32:40.330
and ruined eight bowls of noodles.

32:43.120 --> 32:43.960
Shang Ningyu,

32:45.120 --> 32:45.960
thank you.

32:47.160 --> 32:48.480
Since I was born,

32:49.000 --> 32:50.400
this is my first birthday

32:51.200 --> 32:54.600
having someone willing to make me longevity noodles by hand.

32:57.720 --> 32:58.320
Oh, right.

33:04.160 --> 33:05.020
This is for you.

33:06.240 --> 33:10.000
I wish you peace every year.

33:19.040 --> 33:19.960
What's wrong?

33:22.560 --> 33:23.240
Nothing.

33:24.320 --> 33:25.720
I'm just really touched.

33:28.000 --> 33:28.880
You know

33:29.280 --> 33:30.840
my family sells fruit.

33:32.040 --> 33:33.200
But ever since I was little,

33:33.200 --> 33:34.400
I only ate the rotten

33:34.680 --> 33:35.880
and unsellable ones.

33:35.920 --> 33:37.980
This is the first time someone gave me

33:38.480 --> 33:39.240
such a good

33:40.160 --> 33:41.440
and fresh fruit.

33:43.400 --> 33:46.840
Your mom is pretty harsh on you.

33:48.840 --> 33:50.000
Not exactly harsh.

33:50.440 --> 33:52.480
It's not easy for my mom to raise me and my sister alone,

33:52.480 --> 33:53.340
so she's used to

33:53.600 --> 33:55.680
being frugal.

33:56.440 --> 33:59.400
You always say your dad is gone.

34:00.520 --> 34:02.320
I actually really wanted to ask,

34:03.120 --> 34:05.840
how did he pass away?
